## Summary — root causes of past CI failures

| Failure | Root cause | Prevention |
|---------|-----------|------------|
| `Cannot find module 'web-push'` | deploy.sh had no `pnpm install` | Always check deploy.sh after adding packages |
| `sw.ts` ServiceWorker type errors | SW file included in DOM-lib tsconfig | Exclude all `*.sw.ts` from tsconfig.app.json |
| `Uint8Array<ArrayBufferLike>` | TS5 strict generics, local version more lenient | Use `tsc -b` pre-push; cast `.buffer as ArrayBuffer` |
| Unused variable `qc` | `tsc --noEmit` passed locally, `tsc -b` would have caught it | Use `tsc -b` pre-push |
